<text><body>
<lb n="0189b23"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0189b24"/>
<lb n="0189b25"/>
<lb n="0189b26"/><head type="no">No. 862</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0189b27"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0189023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】享和元年刊長谷寺藏本，【甲】平安時代寫覺海本高山寺藏本，【乙】平安時代寫高山寺藏本，【丙】承元二年行辨傳受本東寺三蜜藏本</note>阿闍梨大曼荼&CB00256;灌頂儀軌</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0189b28"/>
<lb n="0189b29"/><p>爾時金剛手白佛言。世尊若有諸善男子善
<pb ed="T" id="T18.0862.0189c" n="0189c"/>
<lb n="0189c01"/>女人。入此大悲藏生大曼荼羅王三昧耶者。
<lb n="0189c02"/>彼獲幾所福德聚如是說已。佛告金剛手言。
<lb n="0189c03"/>祕密主從初發心。乃至成如來。所有福德聚。
<lb n="0189c04"/>是善男子善女人福德聚。與彼正等。祕密主
<lb n="0189c05"/>以此法門當如是知。彼善男子善女人。從如
<lb n="0189c06"/>來口生佛心之子。若是善男子善女人所在
<lb n="0189c07"/>方所。即為有佛施作佛事。是故祕密主。若樂
<lb n="0189c08"/>欲供養佛者。當供養<note n="0189024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此＝是&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0189024"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">是</rdg></app>善男子善女人。若樂
<lb n="0189c09"/>欲見佛即當觀彼。能摧破魔軍利樂一切。是
<lb n="0189c10"/>故汝等。欲得一切如來真實智慧者。應當一
<lb n="0189c11"/>心修行此法。能速成就一切智故<note place="inline">法華云。淨心信敬佛。淨名
<lb n="0189c12"/>云從無量功德智慧生</note></p>
<lb n="0189c13"/><p>加持五色線索繫其左臂真言曰</p>
<lb n="0189c14"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0189025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">原本真言之傍有梵字書入，今附參照番號而卷末載之 cf. p. 192c</note>（一）唵摩訶<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;日<note n="0189026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【丙】</note><app n="0189026"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app>迦&CB00085;遮&CB00085;日哩俱嚕
<lb n="0189c15"/>&CB00085;日<note n="0189027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="0189027"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app>&CB00085;日<app type="＊" source="0189027"><lem>囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">羅</rdg></app>憾</p>
<lb n="0189c16"/><p>南無金剛界大聖毘盧遮那如來　南<note n="0189028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無＝牟【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="0189028"><lem>無</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">牟</rdg></app>東
<lb n="0189c17"/>方阿&CB00434;如來　南<app type="＊" source="0189028"><lem>無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">牟</rdg></app>南方寶生如來　南<app type="＊" source="0189028"><lem>無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">牟</rdg></app>
<lb n="0189c18"/>西方觀自在王如來　南<app type="＊" source="0189028"><lem>無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">牟</rdg></app>北方不空成就
<lb n="0189c19"/>如來</p>
<lb n="0189c20"/><p>南<app type="＊" source="0189028"><lem>無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">牟</rdg></app>普賢金剛薩埵等盡虛空遍法界微塵
<lb n="0189c21"/>剎土中帝<note n="0189029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">綱＝網【丙】</note><app n="0189029"><lem>綱</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">網</rdg></app>重重三際一切菩薩摩訶薩</p>
<lb n="0189c22"/><p>次復心念此密語。<note n="0189030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔護〕－【甲】</note><app n="0189030"><lem>護</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>持諸弟子。密語曰</p><p type="dharani">（二）
<lb n="0189c23"/>唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>摩訶<note place="inline">引</note>&CB02303;日<note n="0189031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉＝羅【丙】＊</note><app n="0189031"><lem>囉</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>迦<note place="inline">去</note>&CB02303;遮&CB00085;日哩<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0189c24"/>合</note>矩嚧&CB02303;日<app type="＊" source="0189031"><lem>囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB02594;日<app type="＊" source="0189031"><lem>囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">羅</rdg></app><note n="0189032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【丙】</note><app n="0189032"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>菡<note place="inline">引</note></p><p type="inline">次加
<lb n="0189c25"/>持塗香塗諸弟子掌中。真言曰</p><p type="dharani">（三）唵<note place="inline">引</note>&CB02594;日
<lb n="0189c26"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>巘<note n="0189033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">弟＝第【丙】</note><app n="0189033"><lem>弟</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">第</rdg></app>虐</p><p type="inline">塗香時告言。願汝等悉具
<lb n="0189c27"/>一切如來戒定慧解脫解脫知見之香</p>
<lb n="0189c28"/><p>次<note n="0189034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔加〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189034"><lem>加</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>持白華授與弟子。真言曰</p><p type="dharani">（四）唵<note place="inline">引</note>&CB02594;
<lb n="0189c29"/>日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>補瑟閉<note place="inline">二合</note>唵</p><p type="inline">告言願汝等。得一
<pb ed="T" id="T18.0862.0190a" n="0190a"/>
<lb n="0190a01"/>切如來無盡相海</p>
<lb n="0190a02"/><p>次加持香鑪熏弟子雙手。真言曰</p><p type="dharani">（五）唵&CB02594;
<lb n="0190a03"/>日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>杜<note place="inline">引</note>閉惡</p><p type="inline">告言願汝等。得一切如
<lb n="0190a04"/>來無盡大悲滋潤妙色</p>
<lb n="0190a05"/><p>次加持燈令弟子視。真言曰</p><p type="dharani">（六）<note n="0190001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唵＋（引）&M062403;細註【原】</note><app n="0190001"><lem>唵</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">唵<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app>&CB02594;囉
<lb n="0190a06"/><note place="inline">二合</note>路<note place="inline">引</note>計<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00135;翼<note place="inline">二合引</note></p><p type="inline">告言願汝等。獲得一切
<lb n="0190a07"/>如來等虛空界智慧光明金剛<note n="0190002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">劍＝&CB01894;【丙】＊</note><app n="0190002"><lem>劍</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&CB01894;</rdg></app>真言加持
<lb n="0190a08"/>牛五味<note place="inline">乳酪蘇糞尿相和<note n="0190003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">丙本冠註曰澄瀘漉略出經作淨瀘漉可也</note>澄<note n="0190004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚧＝瀘【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190004"><lem>嚧</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">瀘</rdg></app>漉服之</note></p><p type="dharani">（七）唵&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>嗢那
<lb n="0190a09"/>羯吒</p>
<lb n="0190a10"/><p>令飲真言</p><p type="dharani">（八）唵摩<note n="0190005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＝賀【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190005"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">賀</rdg></app>入&CB00085;&CB00256;吽</p>
<lb n="0190a11"/><p>次以摧破一切煩惱隨煩惱。諸佛甚深智慧
<lb n="0190a12"/>金剛<app type="＊" source="0190002"><lem>劍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&CB01894;</rdg></app>真言或部心真言。加持烏曇阿說
<lb n="0190a13"/><note n="0190006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">陀＝他【丙】＊</note><app n="0190006"><lem>陀</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">他</rdg></app>齒木十指量。香水洗塗<note n="0190007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">熏＋（香）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0190007"><lem>熏</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">熏香</rdg></app>。纏華<note n="0190008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔於〕－【甲】</note><app n="0190008"><lem>於</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>根。
<lb n="0190a14"/>以一<note n="0190009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（拳）＋奉【丙】</note><app n="0190009"><lem>奉</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">拳奉</rdg></app>獻一切諸佛。餘與行者。以不動明加
<lb n="0190a15"/>持一百八。如來牙加持</p>
<lb n="0190a16"/><p>次授於齒木。&CB00230;至授戒處嚼小頭。告問擲齒
<lb n="0190a17"/>木得何方。便是彼方。聖人告如是偈言</p>
<lb n="0190a18"/><lg><l>汝獲無等利</l><l>位同於大我</l>
<lb n="0190a19"/><l>一切諸如來</l><l>此教諸菩薩</l>
<lb n="0190a20"/><l>皆以攝<note n="0190010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝授【丙】</note><app n="0190010"><lem>受</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">授</rdg></app>汝</l><l>成辦於大事</l>
<lb n="0190a21"/><l>汝等於明日</l><l>當得大乘生</l></lg>
<lb n="0190a22"/><p>擲之驗其相<note place="inline">令蹲踞<note n="0190011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">坐＝座【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="0190011"><lem>坐</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">座</rdg></app>嚼面東或北。<note n="0190012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（北）＋向【丙】</note><app n="0190012"><lem>向</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">北向</rdg></app>外不成就。
<lb n="0190a23"/>向內成就。若遠&CB00230;<note n="0190013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夾＝來不【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190013"><lem>夾</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">來不</rdg></app>久成就東方上西中南下。四方多是彼部</note></p>
<lb n="0190a24"/><p>三結修多羅當繫等持臂<note place="inline">五色線。五佛加持。貫攝<note n="0190014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">萬行＝行人【甲】，行【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0190014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">萬行＝行人【甲】，＝行【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190014"><lem>萬行</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">行人</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">行</rdg></app>令住等持臂歷
<lb n="0190a25"/>經僧祇令不失壞故名金剛結</note></p>
<lb n="0190a26"/><p>次夜<note n="0190015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行＝以&M062485;【原】，取&M062403;【原】</note><note n="0190015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">行＝以&M062485;【原】，＝取&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0190015"><lem><sic corr="以" resp="【原】">行</sic></lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">取</rdg></app>赤衣覆其首<note place="inline">以真<note n="0190016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＋（王）【甲】</note><app n="0190016"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">言王</rdg></app>及不動尊真言加持一百八遍</note>掩閉
<lb n="0190a27"/>一切諸惡趣門。能開清淨五眼成就</p>
<lb n="0190a28"/><p>結三昧耶契。口<note n="0190017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">授＝受&M062403;【丙】</note><app n="0190017"><lem>授</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【丙】">受</rdg></app>此密言</p><p type="dharani">（九）三<note n="0190018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">昧＝摩【丙】＊</note><app n="0190018"><lem>昧</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">摩</rdg></app>耶薩怛
<pb ed="T" id="T18.0862.0190b" n="0190b"/>
<lb n="0190b01"/>&CB00680;<note place="inline">三<note n="0190019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＝反【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0190019"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">反</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0190b02"/><p>ㄙ即令&CB00594;忍願二度為針。引入壇門中。三遍
<lb n="0190b03"/>授此密語曰<note place="inline">金剛<note n="0190020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鉤＝劍【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0190020"><lem>鉤</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">劍</rdg></app>真言引入</note></p><p type="dharani">（十）三<app type="＊" source="0190018"><lem>昧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">摩</rdg></app>耶吽<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0190b04"/><p>應告言。汝今<app><lem>已</lem><rdg wit="【大】">己</rdg></app>入如來眷屬部中。我今令汝
<lb n="0190b05"/>生金剛智。汝由此智故。當得一切如來最勝
<lb n="0190b06"/>成就。及諸世間出世間一切悉地事業皆悉
<lb n="0190b07"/>成就。汝又不應於未入壇場受灌頂人前說
<lb n="0190b08"/>此法事。汝若說者非但違失汝三昧耶。亦自
<lb n="0190b09"/>招殃咎耳。師應<note n="0190021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">堅＝&CB00594;【丙】</note><app n="0190021"><lem>堅</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00594;</rdg></app>結金剛薩埵<note n="0190022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慧＝惠【丙】＊</note><app n="0190022"><lem>慧</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">惠</rdg></app>契。置弟
<lb n="0190b10"/>子頂上告言。此是金剛薩埵三昧耶契。汝若
<lb n="0190b11"/>輒向未受灌頂人說者。令汝頭破裂。汝於我
<lb n="0190b12"/>所莫生輕慢。應當深生敬信。汝於我身。當如
<lb n="0190b13"/>金剛薩埵想。我所教誨。當盡奉行。若不爾者。
<lb n="0190b14"/>自招殃禍。或令中<note n="0190023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夭＝&CB04361;【丙】</note><app n="0190023"><lem>夭</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&CB04361;</rdg></app>死墮地獄。汝應慎之。
<lb n="0190b15"/>師欲令金剛薩埵入其弟子身心。即結金剛
<lb n="0190b16"/>薩埵契告言。此是金剛薩埵三昧耶。願入汝
<lb n="0190b17"/>身心成無上金剛智。誦此密語曰</p><p type="dharani">（十一）唵<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0190b18"/>&CB02594;日囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>吠<note n="0190024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0190024"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>奢<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0190025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">噁＝惡【丙】</note><app n="0190025"><lem>噁</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">惡</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0190b19"/><p>次結忿怒金剛拳。以忍願二度相鉤。誦上大
<lb n="0190b20"/>乘三昧耶百字密語。唱己掣開上契。由此密
<lb n="0190b21"/>語功能力故。能令弟子入金剛智證殊勝<app type="＊" source="0190022"><lem>慧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">惠</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0190b22"/>由此智故悉能獲得。知一切眾生若干種心。
<lb n="0190b23"/>能知世間三<note n="0190026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">丙本傍註曰種略出經作世</note>種事業。能堅固菩提心。能滅
<lb n="0190b24"/>一切苦惱離一切怖畏。一切<note n="0190027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">眾＋（生）【丙】</note><app n="0190027"><lem>眾</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">眾生</rdg></app>惡不能為害。
<lb n="0190b25"/>一切如來同共加持。一切悉地皆悉現前。諸
<lb n="0190b26"/>未曾有安樂勝事不<note n="0190028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">求＝得【丙】</note><app n="0190028"><lem>求</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">得</rdg></app>自得。汝當深自慶幸。
<lb n="0190b27"/>我今為汝略說功德勝事。於一切地位諸解
<lb n="0190b28"/>脫門神通門三摩地門陀羅尼門波羅<note n="0190029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蜜＝密【丙】</note><app n="0190029"><lem>蜜</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">密</rdg></app>門
<lb n="0190b29"/>十力無畏不共法等。由此法故悉當獲得。所
<pb ed="T" id="T18.0862.0190c" n="0190c"/>
<lb n="0190c01"/>有未曾見聞。百千契經甚深義理自然能解。
<lb n="0190c02"/>汝當不久自當證得諸佛真實智慧。何況下
<lb n="0190c03"/>劣諸餘悉地。作是語已。次當問言。汝見何等
<lb n="0190c04"/>境界<note place="inline">此下有摧罪明等記之</note>次第摧破諸罪已。復想以諸佛
<lb n="0190c05"/>光明淨彼身心。四方阿&CB00434;鞞等。上方大日如
<lb n="0190c06"/>來等。皆放清淨光明。下方想金剛雄<note place="inline">上<note n="0190030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔呼〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190030"><lem>呼</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note><note n="0190031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&SD-DA74;＝&SD-E17C;【乙】</note><app n="0190031"><lem><term lang="san-sd">&SD-DA74;</term></lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&SD-E17C;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0190c07"/>字。放忿怒光明而摧破之。作是法時。能令彼
<lb n="0190c08"/>等必定得見善相。當知彼罪障消滅。若彼罪
<lb n="0190c09"/>極重不見好相。<note n="0190032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">師＝即&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0190032"><lem>師</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">即</rdg></app>應為說真實伽<app type="＊" source="0190006"><lem>陀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">他</rdg></app>令其
<lb n="0190c10"/>覺悟頌曰</p>
<lb n="0190c11"/><lg><l>普賢真身遍一切</l><l>能為世間自在王</l>
<lb n="0190c12"/><l>無始無終無生滅</l><l>性相常住等虛空</l>
<lb n="0190c13"/><l>一切眾生所有心</l><l>堅固菩提名薩埵</l>
<lb n="0190c14"/><l>心住不動三摩地</l><l>精勤決定名金剛</l>
<lb n="0190c15"/><l>我今說此誠實言</l><l>唯願世尊<note n="0190033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">扶＝符【甲】【乙】【丙】，丙本冠註曰符略出經作扶，六卷經作赴</note><app n="0190033"><lem>扶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">符</rdg></app><note n="0190033" place="foot" type="rest">丙本冠註曰符略出經作扶，六卷經作赴</note>本願</l>
<lb n="0190c16"/><l>為利眾生諸悉地</l><l>慈悲哀愍願加持</l></lg>
<lb n="0190c17"/><p>說<note n="0190034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝此【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190034"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">此</rdg></app>語已。復結金剛入契。誦<note n="0190035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&SD-CFD4;＝&SD-CFC6;&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0190035"><lem><term lang="san-sd">&SD-CFD4;</term></lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&SD-CFC6;</rdg></app><note n="0190036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（噁）&M062403;＋字【原】</note><app n="0190036"><lem>字</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">噁字</rdg></app>密語一
<lb n="0190c18"/>百八遍。結金剛縛。以禪智度捻檀<app type="＊" source="0190022"><lem>慧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">惠</rdg></app>度本
<lb n="0190c19"/>間。以進力度少屈相<note n="0190037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拄＝跓【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190037"><lem>拄</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">跓</rdg></app>是也。如是作法已。
<lb n="0190c20"/>若不見好相者。但應引入<note n="0190038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">授＝受【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190038"><lem>授</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">受</rdg></app>三昧耶。<note n="0190039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔不應〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0190039"><lem>不應</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0190c21"/>與其灌頂　次與當<note n="0190040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔為〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190040"><lem>為</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>受此密語三遍<term lang="san-sd">&SD-A67A;&SD-A5E5;
<lb n="0190c22"/>&SD-A5F1;</term>明莫加<term lang="san-sd">&SD-DA49;&SD-A6A9;</term>便誦<term lang="san-sd">&SD-DA44;&SD-A559;&SD-A47C;</term>加入佛三昧<note n="0190041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔耶〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190041"><lem>耶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0190c23"/>明</p><p type="dharani">（十二）唵&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>底車&CB02594;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>穀</p>
<lb n="0190c24"/><p>誦已令擲其華。華所著處。便受彼部尊密語。
<lb n="0190c25"/>當速成就<note place="inline">花墮佛面佛眼等尊成就。墮佛中分成
<lb n="0190c26"/>就心真言。花墮佛下分成就使者真言</note></p>
<lb n="0190c27"/><p>次念此密語三遍。令弟子所結三昧耶印。於
<lb n="0190c28"/>其心上解之。密語曰<note place="inline">願金剛薩埵。常住堅固加持我心。願<note n="0190042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">授＝受【丙】</note><app n="0190042"><lem>授</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">受</rdg></app>與我一切悉地</note>
<lb n="0190c29"/>金剛解脫真言</p><p type="dharani">（十三）唵<note place="inline">引</note>底瑟<note n="0190043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佗＝&CB01260;【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190043"><lem>佗</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&CB01260;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB02594;日
<pb ed="T" id="T18.0862.0191a" n="0191a"/>
<lb n="0191a01"/><app type="＊" source="0189031"><lem>囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00135;哩<note place="inline">二合</note>住<note place="inline"><note n="0191001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">宅＋（母）&M062485;【原】，〔宅反〕&M062403;－【原】</note><note n="0191001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔宅反〕&M062403;－【原】，宅＋（母）&M062485;【原】</note><app n="0191001"><lem><sic corr="宅母反" resp="【原】">宅反</sic></lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">&lac;</rdg></app>引</note>迷<note place="inline">引</note>婆<note place="inline">去</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二</note>舍<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0191a02"/><note n="0191002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">濕&CB00085;＝溼縛【丙】</note><app n="0191002"><lem>濕&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">溼縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0191003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00107;＝姤【丙】</note><app n="0191003"><lem>&CB00107;</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">姤</rdg></app><note place="inline"><note n="0191004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＋（侘）【甲】</note><app n="0191004"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">引侘</rdg></app></note>迷婆<note place="inline">去</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">三</note>紇哩<note place="inline">二合</note>捺<note n="0191005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">琰＝&CB13714;【甲】</note><app n="0191005"><lem>琰</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB13714;</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0191a03"/>迷<note place="inline">引</note>遏<note n="0191006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">丙本冠註曰略出金剛頂地下皆有底</note>地瑟佗<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">四</note>薩&CB00085;悉地<note place="inline"><note n="0191007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">土萆＝二草【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0191007"><lem>土萆</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">二草</rdg></app>反</note>攝迷<note place="inline">一</note>&CB00425;
<lb n="0191a04"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0191008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">丙本冠註曰拽略出經作野，金剛頂作也</note>拽車<note place="inline">五</note>吽<note place="inline">引</note>賀賀賀賀穀<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">六</note></p>
<lb n="0191a05"/><p>次誦此密語。解所掩<note n="0191009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">眼＝服【丙】</note><app n="0191009"><lem>眼</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">服</rdg></app>物。密語曰<note place="inline">所擲花安頂上。薩埵攝
<lb n="0191a06"/>受。汝疾成諸悉地</note></p><p type="dharani">（十四）唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>&CB02594;日<app type="＊" source="0189031"><lem>囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>薩<note n="0191010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怛&CB00085;＝怛縛【丙】＊</note><app n="0191010"><lem>怛&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">怛縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0191a07"/><note n="0191011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">丙本傍註曰娑略出經金剛頂經作薩</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>延帝<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00135;<note n="0191012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">丙本傍註曰曳金剛頂作耶</note>曳<note place="inline">二合</note>斫乞&CB00034;<note place="inline">二合<note n="0191013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">彈＝&CB13799;【丙】</note><app n="0191013"><lem>彈</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&CB13799;</rdg></app>舌引半呼上</note>
<lb n="0191a08"/><note n="0191014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔娜伽去〕－【甲】，娜伽去＝加去【乙】，伽去【丙】</note><note n="0191014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔娜伽去〕－【甲】，娜伽去＝加去【乙】，＝伽去【丙】</note><app n="0191014"><lem>娜伽<note place="inline">去</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">加去</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">伽去</rdg></app>吒曩<note place="inline">三</note><note n="0191015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（怛）＋答【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0191015"><lem>答</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">怛答</rdg></app>播<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0191016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚧唱＝盧唱【甲】，囉烏娜二&M062485;【丙】</note><note n="0191016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚧<app><lem resp="CBETA.Maha">嗢</lem><rdg wit="【大】">唱</rdg></app>＝盧唱【甲】，＝囉烏娜二&M062485;【丙】</note><app n="0191016"><lem><sic corr="囉烏娜二" resp="【丙】">嚧嗢</sic></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">盧唱</rdg></app><note place="inline">半引</note>伽<note place="inline">去引</note>吒
<lb n="0191a09"/>野底<note place="inline">四</note>薩<note n="0191017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝縛【丙】＊</note><app n="0191017"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">縛</rdg></app>惡乞&CB00034;<note place="inline">二<note n="0191018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（五）細註【丙】</note><app n="0191018"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">合<note place="inline">五</note></rdg></app></note>&CB02594;日<app type="＊" source="0189031"><lem>囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>斫乞
<lb n="0191a10"/>&CB00034;<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0191019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">丙本傍註曰遏金剛頂經作囉</note>遏努怛爛<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">六</note>係<note place="inline">引</note>&CB02594;日<app type="＊" source="0189031"><lem>囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;者<note place="inline">七
<lb n="0191a11"/>金剛薩埵。親自專為汝開於五<note n="0191020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">丙本冠註曰眼下略出經有及字</note>眼無上金剛眼</note></p>
<lb n="0191a12"/><p>次呼弟子遍示壇中諸部事相由此法故。為
<lb n="0191a13"/>一切如來之所攝受護念。金剛薩埵常住其
<lb n="0191a14"/>心中。隨彼所求乃至執金剛身無不獲得。漸
<lb n="0191a15"/>當得入一切如來<note n="0191021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">體性＝性體【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0191021"><lem>體性</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">性體</rdg></app>法中<note place="inline">若見此曼荼羅。無量俱胝劫所積
<lb n="0191a16"/>眾罪業由是悉<note n="0191022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔除〕－【甲】，〔除滅〕－【乙】</note><note n="0191022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔除滅〕－【乙】，〔除〕－【甲】</note><app n="0191022"><lem>除滅</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">滅</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0191a17"/><p>次當引所灌頂者。左足踏<note n="0191023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔華〕－【甲】</note><app n="0191023"><lem>華</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>門右足踏華心。
<lb n="0191a18"/>入天帝方門。華臺上<app type="＊" source="0190011"><lem>坐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">座</rdg></app>。以種種華塗香燒香
<lb n="0191a19"/>燈明幡蓋清妙音樂而為供養。如不辨者隨
<lb n="0191a20"/>力作之。所以爾者。謂此人坐佛位故。復以種
<lb n="0191a21"/>種讚詠歌歎。令其殷重生歡喜心。說此頌曰</p>
<lb n="0191a22"/><lg><l>諸佛&CB00418;史下生時</l><l>釋梵龍神隨侍衛</l>
<lb n="0191a23"/><l>種種勝妙吉祥事</l><l>願汝今時盡能得</l>
<lb n="0191a24"/><l>迦毘羅衛誕釋宮</l><l>龍王&CB00449;沐甘露水</l>
<lb n="0191a25"/><l>諸天供養吉祥事</l><l>願汝灌頂亦如是</l>
<lb n="0191a26"/><l>金剛座上為群生</l><l>後夜降魔成正覺</l>
<lb n="0191a27"/><l>現諸希有吉祥事</l><l>願汝此座悉能成</l>
<lb n="0191a28"/><l>波羅奈苑<note n="0191024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">河＝何【丙】，丙本傍註曰何經作所</note><app n="0191024"><lem>河</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">何</rdg></app><note n="0191024" place="foot" type="rest">丙本傍註曰何經作所</note>莊嚴</l><l>為五仙人開妙法</l>
<lb n="0191a29"/><l>成就無量吉祥事</l><l>願汝今時盡獲得</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T18.0862.0191b" n="0191b"/>
<lb n="0191b01"/><l>諸佛大悲方便海</l><l>普利法界眾生海</l>
<lb n="0191b02"/><l>盡未來際無疲倦</l><l><note n="0191025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">四＝此【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0191025"><lem>四</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">此</rdg></app>無礙智汝當得</l></lg>
<lb n="0191b03"/><p>若更有餘讚頌隨意作之。勸發勝心令生利喜
<lb n="0191b04"/>次應與其灌頂。先想弟子頂有<term lang="san-sd">&SD-CFD3;</term>字。放大光
<lb n="0191b05"/>焰熾然赫<app><lem>奕</lem><rdg wit="【大】">弈</rdg></app>。又想弟子心中有月輪。<note n="0191026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔月〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0191026"><lem>月</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>輪內
<lb n="0191b06"/>有八葉蓮華。於華臺上亦有<term lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC5;</term>字。若得金剛
<lb n="0191b07"/>部。於<term lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC5;</term>字內想有五股金剛。餘部可知。若得
<lb n="0191b08"/>大日即想窣堵波。應想己身如毘盧遮那<note n="0191027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">像＝佛&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0191027"><lem>像</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">佛</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0191b09"/>執弟子所得部瓶。各想其部物體在瓶水內。
<lb n="0191b10"/>如金剛蓮等。各令結其所得部契。置於頂上
<lb n="0191b11"/>誦本部密語七遍。而用灌頂。<note n="0191028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（金剛部灌頂）＋真【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0191028"><lem>真</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">金剛部灌頂真</rdg></app>言曰<note n="0191029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔金剛部灌頂〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0191029"><lem><note place="inline">金剛部灌頂</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0191b12"/><p type="dharani">（十五）唵<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一</note>&CB02594;日<app type="＊" source="0189031"><lem>囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">羅</rdg></app>薩<app type="＊" source="0191010"><lem>怛&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">怛縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合引</note>避詵<note n="0191030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔去〕－【丙】</note><app n="0191030"><lem><note place="inline">去</note></lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>者
<lb n="0191b13"/>吽　唵<note place="inline">引</note>&CB02594;日<app type="＊" source="0189031"><lem>囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">羅</rdg></app>喇<note n="0191031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怛＝怚【丙】＊</note><app n="0191031"><lem>怛</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">怚</rdg></app>曩<note n="0191032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合引〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0191032"><lem><note place="inline">二合引</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>避詵者<app type="＊" source="0191031"><lem>怛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">怚</rdg></app>
<lb n="0191b14"/><note n="0191033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02255;＝恪【甲】，&CB03122;【丙】</note><note n="0191033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB02255;＝恪【甲】，＝&CB03122;【丙】</note><app n="0191033"><lem>&CB02255;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">恪</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&CB03122;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>唵<note place="inline">引</note>&CB02594;日<app type="＊" source="0189031"><lem>囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0191034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">丙本傍註曰&CB00425;納麼經作達磨</note>&CB00425;納<note n="0191035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">磨＝麼【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0191035"><lem>磨</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合<note n="0191036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【丙】＊</note><app n="0191036"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>避詵
<lb n="0191b15"/>者紇哩<note place="inline">二合引</note>唵<note n="0191037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0191037"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB02594;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>羯磨<note place="inline">引</note>避詵者
<lb n="0191b16"/>惡</p><p type="inline">於彼額上想有<note n="0191038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&SD-A64A;&CB00256;＝&CB00256;&SD-A64A;【丙】</note><app n="0191038"><lem><tt rend="inline"><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A64A;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00256;</t></tt></lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00256;&SD-A64A;</rdg></app>字。色如真金。於兩
<lb n="0191b17"/>目上各有<tt rend="inline"><t lang="san-sd"><note n="0191039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&SD-A5FD;＝&SD-A64A;【乙】</note><app n="0191039"><lem>&SD-A5FD;</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&SD-A64A;</rdg></app></t><t lang="chi"><note n="0191040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝囉【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0191040"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">囉</rdg></app><note place="inline">上</note></t></tt><note n="0191041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔字〕－【丙】</note><app n="0191041"><lem>字</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。其色如火上有光焰。
<lb n="0191b18"/><note n="0191042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（其焰）＋其【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0191042"><lem>其</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">其焰其</rdg></app>兩足間想種種色。為法輪相<note n="0191043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">八輻＝以輪【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0191043"><lem>八輻</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">以輪</rdg></app>莊嚴</p>
<lb n="0191b19"/><p>次誦金剛薩埵心真言。加持塗香塗彼胸前。
<lb n="0191b20"/>所以作法加持者。為令弟子如金剛薩埵故</p>
<lb n="0191b21"/><p>次結大日印念本真言。置契於彼心上。<note n="0191044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔次額次喉〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0191044"><lem>次額
<lb n="0191b22"/>次喉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>次頂上。即應諦想一切如來祕密勝上
<lb n="0191b23"/>頭冠加彼頭上。即結如上四種鬘印。各隨其
<lb n="0191b24"/>部法以繫其額。若作阿闍<anchor id="fxT18p0191b06"/>梨灌頂法者。應次
<lb n="0191b25"/>第如上法遍用五瓶。以四種鬘鱗次繫其額
<lb n="0191b26"/>上<note n="0191045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝也【丙】</note><app n="0191045"><lem>已</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0191b27"/><p>次師。以觀羽執五股跋折羅授其雙手。應以
<lb n="0191b28"/>種種方便言詞開誘安慰。為說頌曰</p>
<lb n="0191b29"/><lg><l>諸佛金剛灌頂儀</l><l>汝已如法灌頂竟</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T18.0862.0191c" n="0191c"/>
<lb n="0191c01"/><l>為成如來體性故</l><l>汝應受此金剛杵</l></lg>
<lb n="0191c02"/><p>誦此偈已真言曰</p><p type="dharani">（十六）唵<note place="inline">引<note n="0191046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【丙】</note><app n="0191046"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>&CB02594;日<app type="＊" source="0189031"><lem>囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合引</note>
<lb n="0191c03"/>地&CB00425;底<note place="inline">二</note><note n="0191047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">微＝怛【甲】【乙】，怚【丙】，丙本傍註曰怚怚縛略出經作微怚&CB00680;，金剛頂經作怚&CB00085;麼</note><note n="0191047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">微＝怛【甲】【乙】，＝怚【丙】，丙本傍註曰怚怚縛略出經作微怚&CB00680;，金剛頂經作怚&CB00085;麼</note><app n="0191047"><lem>微</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">怛</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">怚</rdg></app><note n="0191047" place="foot" type="rest">丙本傍註曰怚怚縛略出經作微怚&CB00680;，金剛頂經作怚&CB00085;麼</note>怛<app type="＊" source="0191017"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合引</note>避詵<note place="inline">去</note>者彌<note place="inline">三</note>底瑟
<lb n="0191c04"/><note n="0191048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">侘＝&CB00109;【丙】</note><app n="0191048"><lem>侘</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00109;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB02594;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>三摩耶薩<app type="＊" source="0191031"><lem>怛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">怚</rdg></app>&CB00680;</p><p type="inline">復收
<lb n="0191c05"/>取金剛杵。若是寶部者。又跋折羅上<note n="0191049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔想〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0191049"><lem>想</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>有寶
<lb n="0191c06"/>珠。餘部<note n="0191050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">傚＝倣【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0191050"><lem>傚</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">倣</rdg></app>此。誦前真言時。應改初句金剛
<lb n="0191c07"/>字為寶珠。餘部<note n="0191051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">準＝准【丙】</note><app n="0191051"><lem>準</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">准</rdg></app>此</p>
<lb n="0191c08"/><p>次於弟子本名上<note n="0191052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">加金＝金加【丙】</note><app n="0191052"><lem>加金</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">金加</rdg></app>剛字。<note n="0191053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">丙本傍註曰依經作作</note>依名呼之。應誦
<lb n="0191c09"/>此真言</p><p type="dharani">（十七）唵<note place="inline"><note n="0191054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一＝引一【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0191054"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">引一</rdg></app></note>&CB02594;日<app type="＊" source="0189031"><lem>囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>薩怛<app type="＊" source="0191017"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">縛</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合
<lb n="0191c10"/><app type="＊" source="0191036"><lem>引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>避詵<note n="0191055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔去〕－【丙】</note><app n="0191055"><lem><note place="inline">去</note></lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>者<note place="inline">引</note>彌<note place="inline">二</note>&CB02594;日<app type="＊" source="0189031"><lem>囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>曩麼<note place="inline">引<note n="0191056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入＝三【丙】</note><app n="0191056"><lem>入</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">三</rdg></app></note>避
<lb n="0191c11"/><note n="0191057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曬＝&CB01970;【丙】</note><app n="0191057"><lem>曬</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&CB01970;</rdg></app>訖帝<note n="0191058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝入三【甲】【乙】，入【丙】</note><note n="0191058" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三＝入三【甲】【乙】，＝入【丙】</note><app n="0191058"><lem><note place="inline">三</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">入三</note></rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">入</note></rdg></app><note n="0191059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">系＝糸【甲】【丙】，丙本冠註曰糸略出教王皆作係</note><app n="0191059"><lem>系</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">糸</rdg></app><note n="0191059" place="foot" type="rest">丙本冠註曰糸略出教王皆作係</note>&CB02594;日<app type="＊" source="0189031"><lem>囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">羅</rdg></app>　曩<note place="inline">引</note>麼<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">四</note></p>
<lb n="0191c12"/><p>又以香華種種供具供養所灌頂者。師應執
<lb n="0191c13"/>小金剛杵子。如治眼法拭其兩目而告之言</p>
<lb n="0191c14"/><p>善男子世間醫王。能除眼翳。今日諸佛如來。
<lb n="0191c15"/>為汝開無明翳亦復如是。為令汝得金剛智
<lb n="0191c16"/>慧眼見法實相故</p>
<lb n="0191c17"/><p>次復執鏡令其觀照。為顯諸法性相空寂。說
<lb n="0191c18"/>伽<app type="＊" source="0190006"><lem>陀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">他</rdg></app>曰</p>
<lb n="0191c19"/><lg><l>一切諸法性</l><l>垢淨不可得</l>
<lb n="0191c20"/><l>非實亦非虛</l><l>皆從因緣現</l>
<lb n="0191c21"/><l>應當知諸法</l><l>自性無所依</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T18.0862.0192a" n="0192a"/>
<lb n="0192a01"/><l>汝今真佛子</l><l>廣利諸眾生</l></lg>
<lb n="0192a02"/><p>師於弟子當生恭敬。以此人能紹諸佛種性
<lb n="0192a03"/>故。師應授以商佉而告之言。自今已後諸佛
<lb n="0192a04"/>法輪。汝應轉之。當吹無上法螺。令大法聲遍
<lb n="0192a05"/>一切處。不應於此法中而生疑怖。於諸密語
<lb n="0192a06"/>究竟清淨修行理趣。汝應<note n="0192001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔廣〕－【丙】</note><app n="0192001"><lem>廣</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>為眾生方便開
<lb n="0192a07"/>示。善男子諦聽。若能如是修者。一切如來
<lb n="0192a08"/>皆悉知汝能報佛恩。是故於一切時處。一切
<lb n="0192a09"/>持金剛者之所衛護令汝安樂。次應引起至
<lb n="0192a10"/>大壇前。為說三昧耶令其堅固告言。善男子
<lb n="0192a11"/>汝應堅守正法。設遭逼迫苦惱乃至斷命。不
<lb n="0192a12"/>應捨離修菩提心。於求法人及於財物不應
<lb n="0192a13"/>慳&CB00385;。於諸眾生少不利益事。亦不應作。此是
<lb n="0192a14"/>最上句義聖所行處。我今為汝具足說竟。汝
<lb n="0192a15"/>應隨順如說修行。弟子應自慶幸合掌頂禮。
<lb n="0192a16"/>又執五<note n="0192002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">股＝&CB01263;【甲】</note><app n="0192002"><lem>股</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB01263;</rdg></app>金剛杵而授與之。告言此是諸佛
<lb n="0192a17"/>體性。金剛薩埵手所執者。汝應堅護禁戒常
<lb n="0192a18"/>受持之。弟子受已。授此決定要誓密語。令其
<lb n="0192a19"/>誦之密語曰</p>
<lb n="0192a20"/><p type="dharani">（十八）唵<note place="inline">一引</note>薩&CB00085;怛他<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00617;多悉地&CB02594;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0192a21"/>三<note n="0192003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩＝麼【丙】</note><app n="0192003"><lem>摩</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">麼</rdg></app>耶底瑟<note n="0192004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佗＝侘【丙】</note><app n="0192004"><lem>佗</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">侘</rdg></app><note place="inline"><note n="0192005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二〕－【丙】</note><app n="0192005"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>合</note><note place="inline">二</note>翳<note n="0192006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娑＝沙【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0192006"><lem>娑</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">沙</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0191031"><lem>怛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">怚</rdg></app><note n="0192007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">丙本傍註曰&CB00085;金剛頂作&CB00680;&M062443;六卷本同</note><note n="0192007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">丙本傍註曰&CB00085;金剛頂作&CB00680;<todo/>&M062443;六卷本同</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note><note place="inline">三</note>馱囉
<lb n="0192a22"/>耶<note n="0192008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">丙本傍註曰彌金剛頂作&CB02755;</note>彌<note place="inline">四</note>&CB02594;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>薩<anchor id="fxT18p0192a02"/>怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">五</note>呬呬呬呬吽</p>
<lb n="0192a23"/><p>如是作法己。所有一切曼拏<app type="＊" source="0189031"><lem>囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">羅</rdg></app>祕密三昧耶
<lb n="0192a24"/>智師應教授。若弟子於三昧耶有退失者。師
<lb n="0192a25"/>應遮制勿令毀壞。弟子於師應恭敬尊重。莫
<lb n="0192a26"/>見師短。於同學所莫<note n="0192009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔生〕－【丙】</note><app n="0192009"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>嫌恨。應告之言。汝
<lb n="0192a27"/>於一切眾生常生慈愍。哀矜示誨莫生厭離。
<lb n="0192a28"/>為說偈言</p>
<lb n="0192a29"/><lg><l>三界極重罪</l><l>不過於厭離</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T18.0862.0192b" n="0192b"/>
<lb n="0192b01"/><l>汝於貪欲處</l><l>莫生厭離心</l></lg>
<lb n="0192b02"/><p><note n="0192010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">次＝又【丙】</note><app n="0192010"><lem>次</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">又</rdg></app>欲令弟子堅持歡喜故。復說偈曰</p>
<lb n="0192b03"/><lg><l>此等三昧耶</l><l>諸佛為汝說</l>
<lb n="0192b04"/><l>守持善愛護</l><l>當如保身命</l></lg>
<lb n="0192b05"/><p>弟子受師教己。頂禮師足白言。如師教誨我
<lb n="0192b06"/>誓修行。迴向發願。弟子某甲等。向者己來。
<lb n="0192b07"/>於大悲胎藏大曼荼羅前。聽聞正法生淨信
<lb n="0192b08"/>心。稽請聖賢海會聖眾。歸依三寶懺除罪垢
<lb n="0192b09"/>受佛淨戒。<note n="0192011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">投＝&CB00795;【丙】</note><app n="0192011"><lem>投</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00795;</rdg></app>華有緣。蒙聖攝受。已得灌頂
<lb n="0192b10"/>金剛職號。<note n="0192012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">隨＝墮&M062403;【丙】</note><app n="0192012"><lem>隨</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【丙】">墮</rdg></app>賢聖位功德無邊。塵沙叵算。
<lb n="0192b11"/>總將迴施法界眾生。願皆離苦得安穩樂。捨
<lb n="0192b12"/><note n="0192013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">邪＝耶【甲】</note><app n="0192013"><lem>邪</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">耶</rdg></app>歸正發菩提心。行菩薩道永不退轉。於當
<lb n="0192b13"/>來世一時成佛</p>
<lb n="0192b14"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>金剛界大乘現證甚深祕密瑜伽大曼荼羅大
<lb n="0192b15"/>悲無礙大灌頂<note n="0192014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">戒＝式&M062403;【原】，戒儀＝儀軌【甲】</note><note n="0192014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">戒儀＝儀軌【甲】，戒＝式&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0192014"><lem>戒儀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">儀軌</rdg><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">式儀</rdg></app><note n="0192015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">丙本奧書曰承元二年三月十五日于大補阿闍梨御坊奉傳受，求法沙門行辨，享保丙午春應于教猷僧正之需加墨點畢，雖固恐冥慮將便讀文耳，權僧正兼澄</note></jhead></juan></div1><div1 type="W">
<lb n="0192b16"/><note n="0192016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔消除…地〕二十八字－【丙】</note><app n="0192016" word-count="28"><lem><lg type="W"><l>消除無明<note n="0192017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妄＝忌【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0192017"><lem>妄</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">忌</rdg></app>三業</l><l>現得薩埵心月輪</l>
<lb n="0192b17"/><l>決定不退三密行</l><l>自他圓滿成悉地</l></lg></lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0192b18"/><note n="0192018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔寬政…識〕二百十五字－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0192018" word-count="215"><lem><p>寬政十二年庚申晚秋。為充足豐山印刻
<lb n="0192b19"/>之未滿。據相承之本。且&CB00677;挍四五之別本
<lb n="0192b20"/>而點之</p>
<lb n="0192b21"/><p>　　　河南藥樹山沙門真常誌</p>
<lb n="0192b22"/><p>享和改元辛酉年五月。更以京師智積院
<lb n="0192b23"/>之本挍整。彼奧批云　右阿闍梨灌頂儀
<lb n="0192b24"/>軌一卷。梵文句義舊本所無。今守師授私
<lb n="0192b25"/>加書之。但厥句義全依四卷略出經註。繕
<lb n="0192b26"/>寫之次披閱過數。文苑蕪穢義路不通。推
<lb n="0192b27"/>之祕其事相往往爛脫。因以菅窺猥點一
<lb n="0192b28"/>班。負識遮梨希下雌黃云。元祿庚午三年
<lb n="0192b29"/>中秋念有三日　內州教興徒慧光志<note place="inline">行年二十五</note>
<pb ed="T" id="T18.0862.0192c" n="0192c"/>
<lb n="0192c01"/>如是梵文句義。後之增加。然傳寫久間闕
<lb n="0192c02"/>句義。或唯有梵脫漢譯。待復挍善本　豐
<lb n="0192c03"/>山　總持院沙門快道識</p></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0192019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">長谷寺本奧朱書曰一校加&CB01339;訖，享和癸亥四月十二日，慈順異本奧庇云，右阿闍梨灌頂儀軌一卷梵文句義，舊本所無，今守師授私加書之，但厥句義全依四卷略出經注，繕寫之次披閱過數，文苑蕪穢義路不通，惟之祕其事相往往爛脫，因以管窺猥點一班，負識遮梨希下雌黃云，元祿庚午三年中秋念有三日，內州教興徒慧光志，行年廿五，天明二年仲冬十一日，以慧光大和尚寫本而騰了，宣雄，文政四年辛巳九月九日，以板橋日曜寺本，自手朱再校之了，龍肝</note>
